1. Create account in git hub.
2. Goto the project path in the github.
3. goto code button, then select https and copy the link. (ex: https://github.com/codify-training/Java-full-stack-training.git)
4. In IDE File -> New Window -> Clone git repsitory -> here paste the URL.
5. Then the project starts downlloading.






Terminology:
Check out - Get code from github to your local machine
Checkin - Send your changes to github from your local machine.


Push - Send the changes in your local machine to the github
pull - Bring all the changes from the github to your local.